  "quirks": "Gun economy: Shoot needs a loaded bullet; Gun Throw discards the gun (huge 800 damage if it lands, fires a bullet on hit) and GunReel ('Gun Pull') retrieves it. Hustle is the universal Taunt state: +1 meter on completion but interruptible, so it is only safe with initiative or at long range. Teleport startup/recovery scale with travel distance (5-19f startup, 10-30f IASA). The source scene also contains states not in this community table (TimeSplitter 'Time Splitter', TPStance 'Warp Stance', Foresight, ForesightExplosion 'Time Rift', PointBlank, SpotDodge, ShootDodge2 'Shoot Dodge', ShootDodgeRoll 'Dodge', Guntrick 'Gun Trick'); always trust the runtime legal-move list from LegalMoveEnumerator over this table. Frame data is community-sourced (YomiBot) and may drift from the current patch. ActionType follows the game enum (Movement/Attack/Special/Super/Defense); AirType is the state's usability enum (Grounded/Aerial/Both)."
}
